{"tid":1653021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(警世)今晚唔好再嗌六大訴求呀","createTime":"2019-10-14T02:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T10:55:23.000Z","uid":125168,"like":155,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"7607e1f6e72b467628b88232b1acd8c4498461a1","tid":1653021,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"Five demands<br />\nNot one less!<br />\n<br />\n好多記者㗎今日，盡量唔好集中只嗌trump ,please liberate Hong Kong呢類嘢，美國唔係得總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要汲取之前嘅經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，今晚準時7pm,遮打見，幾點黎都唔會遲，只差你一個"},{"pid":"156cdb95e6ae2d586bc001ebb4c0401e9e6bfea0","tid":1653021,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ad9160a73116aef4cb2fa200803765654af99f","tid":1653021,"uid":11706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f615dfe8a3c683af0d2f53efbc9631450980a53","tid":1653021,"uid":249263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"大家可以用下twitter help 去每日領任務retweet！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DArHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=47484227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKHAaEE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKHAaEE.png&h=6b504c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只要輸入 /task2 就可以知道外國議員外媒名人出左咩重要tweet，大家去retweet啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8KyGMc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8KyGMc.png&h=aeb55a2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做完task2，繼續做埋task1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntask1係普通帳號但都係重要的tweets!<br />\n求retweet!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oySTGM6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoySTGM6.png&h=5c90755c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而task3就係唔直接關香港事，但係同中國人權問題/支爆問題有關的tweets! 歡迎大家去煲大淋火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vz2Xo1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvz2Xo1f.png&h=8f68e83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家響美國過人權法案的時候，<br />\n千祈唔好放棄twitter戰線呀！<br />\n仲有英國話今日會講英女王會講英國版magnitsky Act！<br />\n依家係重要關頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要一人一twitter!!!!!!<br />\n一路retweet一路去集會！"},{"pid":"789a543dda4deda2c25b2aaf68fb783752b6dbfc","tid":1653021,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"92ad9160a73116aef4cb2fa200803765654af99f","tid":1653021,"uid":11706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:08:43.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:10:22.000Z","msg":"大家提下身邊人，唔好嗌錯！"},{"pid":"cd04187fc7b518b5c693b944ef75f37bb2bfadea","tid":1653021,"uid":36471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd0f43fccc7f6d0b3a04a2455f34432b790fa985","tid":1653021,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"幫手正皮留言推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687d53d722c9f359250c3f7928d49521dd2ecc3d","tid":1653021,"uid":169665,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"鬼佬都識舉起一隻手掌知道係5 demands <img src=\"/assets/faces